uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.forms.transition

Interface TransitionFactoryCreator<P extends TransitionFactory>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - type of TransitionProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConfigFormProvider, DynamicFormManager, EmailTransitionFactoryCreator, FormFactoryProviderRegistry, FormRegistry, HeirarchyFormRegistry, LogTransitionProviderFactory, PersonalResponseManager

    public interface TransitionFactoryCreator<P extends TransitionFactory>
    Interface for classes that can generate a TransitionFactory. This is intended for cases where a common set of transitions are implementeded on different target objects. The TransitionFactory is parameterised by the target factory so we use a 2 step creation process.

    spb
